---
title: Soy-Maple Glazed Salmon with Asparagus and Sweet Potato Mash
description: In this weeknight winner, salmon is drizzled with a sweet soy-maple glaze and pan-seared to a crispy finish. It is all finished to perfection with chives, sweet potato mash, and crispy asparagus.
